{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Obviously, you risked your life, but there was a choice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I wanted to survive, but not at any price, and that is a point which I very much wanted to make.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I lived according to that during my whole time in camp, except for that one incident when I was really vicious and nasty and pushed out that one person.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Now, we were-- I just want to describe very quickly the inside of-- I think I told already.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the barracks we had to these bunks, and we had one prickly, straw-filled mattress.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we also had a prickly blanket, individual blanket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One for each of us, which was luxury, in spite of it that they were prickly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in August the central heating was on because there was central heating there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the central heating was on in August.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't on in winter, which wasn't so good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was one thing about the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Also was a very long table, and people did all kinds of things in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now I have no-- haven't found yet any corroboration-- now, I find that there are certain stories which some people tell and others don't tell-- but I found out that it must be because we were working in shifts, and certain things others didn't.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I didn't come across anybody who was in my shift and who remembered one of these odd stories.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For three days we very given-- either three days-- for-- for three days we were given three marks each.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Or four days, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Three or four days, as-- as a payment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Suddenly they said they are going to pay us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
